{"tid":1619013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大愛撚】我要發起全香港係你屋企活動","createTime":"2019-10-04T07:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T16:08:16.000Z","uid":316947,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a9ceb5de68e54b25768f00adea49cc52f9d34aba","tid":1619013,"uid":316947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:09:20.000Z","msg":"有啲小朋友夢遊成日無車搭or點點點返唔到屋企，有時搭校巴返去都好夜了<br />\n又有啲小朋友行街突然吸到二手煙唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，出面又有狗狗吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但無得即時返屋企避<br />\n我身為一啲大愛撚，希望各位小朋友有事嗰陣有安全地方<strong>馬上</strong>休息<br />\n我呼籲各位家長開心些牙你個屋企<br />\n有事嗰陣落街大嗌小朋友返屋企，接啲小朋友返屋企訓下覺，沖個涼，休息一下，等附近狗狗走咗先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要佢地喺全港18區都有屋企返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全香港都係屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ddad9a73a769eed89ee83d0d279a8b04869228","tid":1619013,"uid":253176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:10:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9f0a04abce57beb26a6d16e37c7361a86802409","tid":1619013,"uid":316947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:10:36.000Z","msg":"發夢無位走又有咩好驚，上黎家庭聚會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e44c43ae6ea7edc0b9410d6c2ac2f1c5e3085a","tid":1619013,"uid":215408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:10:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6043882866bf34e1b214ff3d188e8d536d889f36","tid":1619013,"uid":316947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:11:35.000Z","msg":"我要小朋友封撚咗個黨鐵都有屋企返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a267b95b69e1b707de175aff37c7b5d87c144108","tid":1619013,"uid":316947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:18:50.000Z","msg":"我呢啲街坊好中意叫小朋友